#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int t,u,l,i,sum,j,k,flag,ctr,a[]={1,4,6,8,9,10,12,14,15,16,18,20,21,22,24,25,26,27,28,30,32,33,34,35,36};
	scanf("%d",&t);
	while(t--)
	{
		scanf("%d%d",&u,&l);
		ctr=0;
		for (i=u;i<=l;i++)
		{
			j=i;
			sum=0;
			while (j)
			{
				sum+=j%10;
				j/=10;
			}
			flag=0;
			for (k=0;k<25;k++)
				if (sum==a[k])
				{
					flag=1;
					break;
				}
			if (!flag)
				ctr++;
		}
		printf("%d\n",ctr);
	}
	return 0;
}
